OL,3,CPlans to expand Newcastle Airport
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FPlans to expand Newcastle
OL,7,FInternational Airport have been given
OL,8,Fapproval by councillors, with
OL,9,Fpassengers being promised a "smoother
OL,10,Fjourney" through the terminal.
OL,12,FThe three-storey expansion, which was
OL,13,Fsigned off by Newcastle City Council's
OL,14,Fplanning committee, includes plans for
OL,15,Fan enhanced departure lounge and
OL,16,Fbaggage arrival area.
OL,18,FWork on the project could get underway
OL,19,Fas early as the summer, with the aim
OL,20,Fof cutting congestion during peak
OL,21,Fperiods and reducing overcrowding.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
