OL,3,CPlans to expand Newcastle Airport
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FThe Airport's chief executive Nick
OL,7,FJones said: "The international baggage
OL,8,Farrivals area will also be expanded
OL,9,Fand an extra luggage carousel will be
OL,10,Finstalled, helping to deliver a
OL,11,Fsmoother, more seamless journey for
OL,12,Fpassengers.
OL,14,F"This project follows almost #20m of
OL,15,Frecent investment in the Airport,
OL,16,Fincluding resurfacing the runway and
OL,17,Fupgrading many of the catering
OL,18,Ffacilities. We're now looking forward
OL,19,Fto beginning work on the terminal
OL,20,Fextension this summer."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
