OL,6,FThe airport says there will be no
OL,7,Fchange in the flight capacity at the
OL,8,Fairport as a result of the work and
OL,9,Fthat a significant rise in the number
OL,10,Fof passengers is not expected.
OL,12,FCoun Juna Sathian, the council's
OL,13,Fcabinet member for transport, said: "A
OL,14,Fsuccessful airport means a successful
OL,15,FNorth East so I am delighted that
OL,16,Fplanning committee has approved the
OL,17,Fexpansion of the terminal.
