OL,3,CPlans to expand Newcastle Airport
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,F"Enlarging the baggage handling area,
OL,7,Fthe departure lounge and having more
OL,8,Fshops, bars and restaurants will give
OL,9,Fpassengers a more pleasurable
OL,10,Fexperience and allow the airport to
OL,11,Faccommodate increased numbers at busy
OL,12,Ftimes allowing people to move through
OL,13,Fthe airport quickly and more freely.
OL,15,F"This investment is a vote of
OL,16,Fconfidence in our airport, and I look
OL,17,Fforward to work starting soon."
